title: Spacious Lyn-Lake 3 bedroom Avail 9/1
posting_body: ['Large, nice 3 Bedroom apartment on 2nd floor of Lyn-Lake duplex available September 1st for a 1 year lease.', "- All 3 bed rooms are fairly big, this isn't one of those places with 2 big bed rooms and a tiny closet the landlord is trying to claim is a 3rd bedroom.", '- The apartment is in a great area, 1 block from the Wedge Co-op and many major bus lines to downtown and the U.   It is walking distance to downtown, Lake of the Isles, and Calhoun Square.', "Some in the neighborhood don't even have cars.", '- If you do have a car, very easy access to Uptown, downtown, 94, 394, and 35W.  The unit includes 2 off street parking spaces, with enough room to squeeze in a 3rd car when there is snow-street bans on parking.', '- Apartment is 1450 square feet with a very large kitchen, good sized living room, and 1 bathroom.', '- Original hardwood floors everywhere except tiled kitchen and bathroom.', '- Kitchen has a dishwasher.', '- Shared Free laundry in the basement and tons of room for storage.', '- Building is wired for US Internet Fiber service - cheap, fast internet!', "- The one thing this place doesn't have is central air, you'll need to bring your window units.", 'Rent includes water and electric.', 'You pay gas.', 'Email to set up an appointment to see apartment.', "The photos don't do this place justice - whenever this unit comes up for rent, it usually is rented before I can update the pictures!"]
